long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Rotare is a fun arcade game where we try to move forward and score points by changing the ball's direction in a restricted area.
Limited space in the game. We are trying to move with a ball in this area. Move forward by changing the direction of the ball and getting points. We continue the game by maintaining our high score goal with the points we have achieved. Rotare has emerged as a skill game. That has prepared us in mind for those who love children's games and challenge us.
